      "title": "Diagnostic probes: TCP handshake & DNS lookup time",
      "description": "Captured during a triggered diagnostic run. TCP handshake time exercises the real path independent of ICMP (many ISPs deprioritize pings), and DNS lookup time catches resolution problems that masquerade as general slowness.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "justrebootit-prometheus" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 71 },
